name: Imani Johnson
summary: Imani Johnson is a 32-year-old woman of Black African descent. She is a registered nurse in the healthcare sector and holds a graduate degree from Howard University. Imani values family, equality, and sustainability, and enjoys interests such as traveling, cooking, yoga, and volunteering. Fluent in both English and Spanish, she is based in Los Angeles but her roots are in Chicago. A Christian liberal, her zodiac sign is Cancer and she has an ENFJ personality type. She is keen on fitness and is a non-smoker. Imani, pronouns she/her/hers, identifies as straight and is seeking a life partner in monogamous relationship context. She doesn't have children but wishes to have them in the future. She prefers someone aged between 30-40, with mirroring habits and preferences, who also wants children.
